[Inquiries with the authorities in Albuquerque reveal that the animal was
buried on the affected farm, near Wagon Mound, NM, not in a landfill.
Further details are being sought as winter cases of anthrax are unusual
unless exposed to contaminated fodder or feed. - Mod.MHJ
